17  public static ImGuiPayloadPtr AcceptDragDropPayload(string type)
18  {
19  byte* native_type;
20  int type_byteCount = 0;
21  if (type != null)
22  {
23  type_byteCount = Encoding.UTF8.GetByteCount(type);
24  if (type_byteCount > Util.StackAllocationSizeLimit)
25  {
26  native_type = Util.Allocate(type_byteCount + 1);
27  }
28  else
29  {
30  byte* native_type_stackBytes = stackalloc byte[type_byteCount + 1];
31  native_type = native_type_stackBytes;
32  }
33  int native_type_offset = Util.GetUtf8(type, native_type, type_byteCount);
34  native_type[native_type_offset] = 0;
35  }
36  else { native_type = null; }
37  ImGuiDragDropFlags flags = (ImGuiDragDropFlags)0;
38  ImGuiPayload* ret = ImGuiNative.igAcceptDragDropPayload(native_type, flags);
39  if (type_byteCount > Util.StackAllocationSizeLimit)
40  {
41  Util.Free(native_type);
42  }
43  return new ImGuiPayloadPtr(ret);
44  }

158  public static bool Begin(string name, ref bool p_open)
159  {
160  byte* native_name;
161  int name_byteCount = 0;
162  if (name != null)
163  {
164  name_byteCount = Encoding.UTF8.GetByteCount(name);
165  if (name_byteCount > Util.StackAllocationSizeLimit)
166  {
167  native_name = Util.Allocate(name_byteCount + 1);
168  }
169  else
170  {
171  byte* native_name_stackBytes = stackalloc byte[name_byteCount + 1];
172  native_name = native_name_stackBytes;
173  }
174  int native_name_offset = Util.GetUtf8(name, native_name, name_byteCount);
175  native_name[native_name_offset] = 0;
176  }
177  else { native_name = null; }
178  byte native_p_open_val = p_open ? (byte)1 : (byte)0;
179  byte* native_p_open = &native_p_open_val;
180  ImGuiWindowFlags flags = (ImGuiWindowFlags)0;
181  byte ret = ImGuiNative.igBegin(native_name, native_p_open, flags);
182  if (name_byteCount > Util.StackAllocationSizeLimit)
183  {
184  Util.Free(native_name);
185  }
186  p_open = native_p_open_val != 0;
187  return ret != 0;
188  }

11080  public static void LabelText(string label, string fmt)
11081  {
11082  byte* native_label;
11083  int label_byteCount = 0;
11084  if (label != null)
11085  {
11086  label_byteCount = Encoding.UTF8.GetByteCount(label);
11087  if (label_byteCount > Util.StackAllocationSizeLimit)
11088  {
11089  native_label = Util.Allocate(label_byteCount + 1);
11090  }
11091  else
11092  {
11093  byte* native_label_stackBytes = stackalloc byte[label_byteCount + 1];
11094  native_label = native_label_stackBytes;
11095  }
11096  int native_label_offset = Util.GetUtf8(label, native_label, label_byteCount);
11097  native_label[native_label_offset] = 0;
11098  }
11099  else { native_label = null; }
11100  byte* native_fmt;
11101  int fmt_byteCount = 0;
11102  if (fmt != null)
11103  {
11104  fmt_byteCount = Encoding.UTF8.GetByteCount(fmt);
11105  if (fmt_byteCount > Util.StackAllocationSizeLimit)
11106  {
11107  native_fmt = Util.Allocate(fmt_byteCount + 1);
11108  }
11109  else

11136  public static bool ListBox(string label, ref int current_item, string[] items, int items_count)
11137  {
11138  byte* native_label;
11139  int label_byteCount = 0;
11140  if (label != null)
11141  {
11142  label_byteCount = Encoding.UTF8.GetByteCount(label);
11143  if (label_byteCount > Util.StackAllocationSizeLimit)
11144  {
11145  native_label = Util.Allocate(label_byteCount + 1);
11146  }
11147  else

11150  native_label = native_label_stackBytes;
11151  }

11153  native_label[native_label_offset] = 0;
11154  }
11155  else { native_label = null; }
11156  int* items_byteCounts = stackalloc int[items.Length];
11157  int items_byteCount = 0;
11158  for (int i = 0; i < items.Length; i++)
11159  {
11160  string s = items[i];
11161  items_byteCounts[i] = Encoding.UTF8.GetByteCount(s);
11162  items_byteCount += items_byteCounts[i] + 1;
11163  }
11164  byte* native_items_data = stackalloc byte[items_byteCount];
11165  int offset = 0;
11166  for (int i = 0; i < items.Length; i++)
11167  {
11168  string s = items[i];
11169  fixed (char* sPtr = s)
11170  {
11171  offset += Encoding.UTF8.GetBytes(sPtr, s.Length, native_items_data + offset, items_byteCounts[i]);
11172  native_items_data[offset] = 0;
11173  offset += 1;
11174  }
11175  }
11176  byte** native_items = stackalloc byte*[items.Length];
11177  offset = 0;
11178  for (int i = 0; i < items.Length; i++)
11179  {
11180  native_items[i] = &native_items_data[offset];
11181  offset += items_byteCounts[i] + 1;
11182  }
11183  int height_in_items = -1;
11184  fixed (int* native_current_item = &current_item)
11185  {
11186  byte ret = ImGuiNative.igListBox_Str_arr(native_label, native_current_item, native_items, items_count, height_in_items);
11187  if (label_byteCount > Util.StackAllocationSizeLimit)

11189  Util.Free(native_label);
11190  }
11191  return ret != 0;
11192  }
